==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Corpulency
<hw>Cor"pu*len*cy</hw> <pr>(k?r"p?-l<it>e</it>n-s?)</pr>, }</mhw>
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>corpulentia</ets>: cf. F.
<ets>corpulence</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Excessive fatness; fleshiness; obesity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Thickness; density; compactness.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The heaviness and <qex>corpulency</qex> of water requiring a great
force to divide it.</q> <rj><qau>Ray.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Corpulent</ent>⟦br⟧
